00:01:35.600 --> 00:01:38.640
Dia pergi menemui nenekmu
di Rumah Sabharwal.

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:42.560
Benar-benar?
- Ya.  Saya terlambat ke kantor.

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.320
Oke, Bu.  Hati-hati,
sayang kamu.

00:01:49.440 --> 00:01:50.960
Kaashvi.. Nenek..

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.280
Luar biasa!

00:01:57.720 --> 00:01:59.640
Kaashvi telah berhenti
menerima panggilan.

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:01.640
Biarkan aku menelepon nenek.

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:07.440
Arjun menelepon!

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:08.800
Salam, Nenek.

